## Issue

Several orders were not linked to valid customer records, causing data integrity concerns.

## Investigation

Performed a LEFT JOIN between orders and customers to identify orphaned orders without corresponding customer records.

## Root Cause

Orders referenced customer IDs that did not exist in the customer table.

## Resolution

Identified affected orders and recommended correction of invalid customer references.

## Preventive Action

Enforce referential integrity through foreign key constraints and validation checks during data entry.
